strings.Value: "It feels strange to say it, but you and I have more in common than it seems. You live for pleasures, new feelings and sensations... And gnomes live for the same thing – otherwise we're overtaken by the Bleaching, soon followed by death."
"A curious perspective... You might even have a point. If so – why don't you submit to Urgathoa? I guarantee you a host of new sensations!"
